# 接口名称: 藏品价格查询
# 来源文档: spider_process.md
# 说明: 查询指定藏品的市场总额、成交量、最低价等汇总指标。

@baseUrl = https://api.x-metash.cn

### 藏品价格查询
POST {{baseUrl}}/h5/archive/archiveMarket
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timeType": 0,
  "archiveId": 54866
}

### 示例响应
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "msg": "成功",
#   "data": {
#     "marketAmount": 497280.0,
#     "marketAmountRate": 2.89,
#     "dealCount": 39,
#     "dealCountRate": 22.67,
#     "minPrice": 82.88,
#     "minPriceRate": 2.89
#   }
# }
